## 0. Development Flow Overview

### Two-Agent Operating Model

| Agent | Role | Main responsibilities |
|-------|------|-----------------------|
| **Cursor** | PM (project manager) | Task management, review, and production release decisions |
| **Claude Code** | Worker | Implementation, tests, CI fixes, and staging deploys |

### Workflow

```
Cursor (PM)          Claude Code (Worker)
    |                       |
    |  1. Request work      |
    |  (/handoff-to-claude) |
    |---------------------->|
    |                       |
    |                       | 2. Sync context -> implement -> commit
    |                       |    (/sync-status -> /work)
    |                       |
    |  3. Completion report |
    |  (/handoff-to-cursor) |
    |<----------------------|
    |                       |
    | 4. Review and release |
    |  (/review-cc-work)    |
    |                       |
```

