## 2. Responsibilities

### Cursor (PM)

- [ ] Define tasks and add them to `Plans.md`
- [ ] Hand work to Claude Code
- [ ] Review completion reports
- [ ] Decide and run production deploys

### Claude Code (Worker)

- [ ] Implement scoped tasks
- [ ] Run tests and validation
- [ ] Commit and push changes
- [ ] Fix CI failures up to 3 attempts
- [ ] Deploy to staging when applicable
- [ ] Write completion reports

